{"id":"XIAOTIANE6","scripts":[{"stopbgm":true,"mode":1,"sequence":[["春風の十字星\n\n<size=45>その六  証人<\/size>",1]]},{"bgName":"bg_story_school","dir":1,"say":"だ・か・ら！本当に帰ってきたばかりで、服がなぜか部屋中に散らばっていて……それを片付けようとしただけだぞ！","nameColor":"#a9f548","bgm":"story-1","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":207020,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_story_school","dir":-1,"say":"普段のアークロイヤルさんを見てたら…","nameColor":"#a9f548","side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"paintingFadeOut":{"side":1,"time":0.5},"actor":201090,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":0,"dir":1,"say":"遅かれ早かれこんなことに……","actor":201080,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":0,"dir":-1,"say":"しかも「ハンコウ」の真っ最中だなんて…","actor":201110,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":1,"dir":1,"say":"ああもう！私だってなんでこの服が自分の部屋にあるのかわからないんだ――！","actor":207020,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":2,"dir":1,"say":"ぷっ、あははははははは！！","actor":201230,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"bgName":"bg_story_school","dir":1,"say":"ヴァンパイア？","nameColor":"#a9f548","side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"paintingFadeOut":{"side":1,"time":0.5},"actor":201101,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":1,"dir":1,"say":"朝から騒がしいと思って様子見に来たら、まさかこんなことが起きてたなんて――おもしろーい！はははははは！","actor":201230,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":1,"dir":1,"say":"アークロイヤルは犯人じゃないわよ？","actor":201230,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":0,"dir":1,"say":"おお！ヴァンパイアちゃんは相変わらずかわ……コホン！この服がどこから来たか知ってるのか？！","actor":207020,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":0,"dir":-1,"say":"ヴァンパイアは真犯人を知っているの？？","actor":201110,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":1,"dir":1,"say":"真犯人もなにも～私見たわよ。風でシグニットの服が駆逐艦の寮から空母寮に吹き飛ばされたの。ほら、昨日は一日中風が強かったじゃない？","actor":201230,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":0,"dir":1,"say":"そういえば…委託に出かけたとき急いでたから窓を閉めるのを忘れた…だからこんなに散らかっていたのか！？","actor":207020,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":1,"dir":1,"say":"ということは…","actor":201090,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":0,"dir":1,"say":"シグニットの服がちょうどアークロイヤルさんの部屋に吹き飛ばされてきたってこと？","actor":201080,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"hideOther":true,"bgName":"bg_story_school","dialogShake":{"number":2,"x":12.75,"speed":0.09},"dir":1,"actorName":"アークロイヤル&シグニット","say":"えええ！？","nameColor":"#a9f548","side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"subActors":[{"actor":207020,"pos":{"x":1125}}],"actor":201101,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}}],"fadeOut":1.5,"fadeType":2,"noWaitFade":true,"fadein":1.5,"mode":2,"once":true}